Use the standard library
This is how to pairs_sum_to_zero of l:
  Remember that count is 0
  Remember that i is 0
  Do this l's length times:
    Remember that first is item i in l
    Remember that j is sum of i and 1
    Do this l's length times:
      When j is less than l's length, then:
        When sum of first and item j in l is 0, then:
          Increase count by 1
        End when
        Increase j by 1
      But, if not:
        Leave the loop
      End when
    End do
    Increase i by 1
  End do
  The answer is count
Now you know